Nengi has promised to hook Kiddwaya up with a decent girl from her hone state, Bayelsa. She said this in the kitchen on Friday night while describing Kidd as husband material. Kiddwaya was in a ‘realtionship’ with disqualified Erica but has moved on since she left. “Kidd, you are good. You are husband material. Don’t worry, I’ll find you a decent Bayelsa girl when we leave the house,” Nengi told Kiddwaya. Nengi, who is perceived to be interested in Kidd, has dispelled the accusation in her latest utterance.